/////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
// How to write the COM object.
/////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

1) Create the COM class as usual using the ATl Object Wizard.


2) Add the following macro to this class's new .h file just above the 
DECLARE_REGISTRY_RESOURCEID macro:

DECLARE_CLASSFACTORY_SINGLETON(CWzd)

where CWzd is the name of the class.



